---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import { partners, topicColumns } from '../../constants';

import ghsLogo from '../../assets/partners/ghs.jpeg';
import sdgImage from '../../assets/programs/sdg.png';
import talkImage from '../../assets/programs/talk.jpeg';
import womanImage from '../../assets/programs/woman.jpg';
import ghanaLogo from '../../assets/programs/ghana.png';

const videoConfig = {
  title: "Communication During a Public Health Crisis: Using Talking Books",
  youtubeId: "2P_XiIqyTIo?si=1qWB2ei-3SSIiiPu"
};
---

<div class="min-h-screen">
    <section class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 md:py-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4 md:mb-8">Partnering for Impact</h2>
        <p class="max-w-3xl text-base md:text-lg text-center mx-auto px-4">
          Some of the <a href="/partners" class="text-blue-500 font-bold hover:underline">partners</a> we work with include {partners.map((partner, index) => (
            <>
              {partner.name}{index < partners.length - 1 ? ', ' : ''}
            </>
          ))}
        </p>
    </section>
  
    <section class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 mb-4">
        <div class="relative w-full pb-[56.25%]">
          <iframe
            class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full shadow-lg"
            src={`https://www.youtube.com/embed/${videoConfig.youtubeId}`}
            title={videoConfig.title}
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
            allowfullscreen
          ></iframe>
        </div>
    </section>
  
    <section class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pb-4 bg-white">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <Image 
          src={ghsLogo}
          alt="Ghana Health Service Logo" 
          width={128}
          height={128}
          class="w-24 h-24 md:w-32 md:h-32 mb-6 md:mb-8"
        />
        <blockquote class="max-w-3xl text-xl md:text-2xl text-center mx-auto mb-4 px-4">
          "The Talking Book builds up so much trust. Community members now have access to clear health messages in their own language, and they are learning and sharing that information with others."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="text-center mx-auto px-4">
          Florence Angsomwine, Jirapa Municipal Health Director, Ghana Health Service
        </p>
        <div class="text-center mt-6 md:mt-8">
          <a href="https://studio.youtube.com/video/bfBIPhkxlV8/edit" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">
            Watch our COVID-19 Response partnership documentary &gt;
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="w-full mt-12 md:mt-20">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 mb-8 md:mb-12">
        <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
          <Image 
            src={sdgImage}
            alt="Multi-sector solution illustration" 
            width={800}
            height={600}
            class="w-full h-full object-cover shadow-lg"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="bg-blue-50 w-full h-full p-6 md:p-8 md:pt-16 text-center order-1 md:order-2">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 md:mb-6">A Multi-Sector Solution</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 px-4">
            Most of our partners are working on multisectoral projects. With the Talking Book, 
            we can share knowledge about many topics and address critical, interconnected issues, 
            such as climate change and gender equity.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-12 px-4 md:px-32">
        {topicColumns.map((column) => (
          <ul class="space-y-2 md:space-y-3 list-disc pl-6 text-semibold">
            {column.map((topic) => (
              <li class="text-gray-800 py-1">{topic.name}</li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="w-full pt-8 md:pt-16 bg-white">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="p-4 md:p-8 text-center md:mt-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 md:mb-6">Culturally-Relevant Content</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 md:mb-8 mx-auto px-4 max-w-xl">
            We work with subject experts, musicians, and theater groups to create messages, including songs, dramas, and interviews. Our team has produced Talking Book audio content in more than a dozen languages.
          </p>
          <button class="bg-white border-2 border-black px-6 py-2 font-medium hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
            LEARN MORE
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="relative h-[300px] md:h-[500px]">
          <Image 
            src={talkImage}
            alt="Recording an interview" 
            width={800}
            height={500}
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="w-full">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="relative h-[300px] md:h-[500px]">
          <Image 
            src={womanImage}
            alt="Community facilitation session" 
            width={800}
            height={500}
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 md:p-8 text-center md:mt-16">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 md:mb-6">Community Facilitation</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6 md:mb-8 mx-auto px-4 max-w-xl">
            We partner with communities to improve learning, engagement, and impact. We want to see the hard work of smallholder farmers and rural families lead to better health, income, equity, and education.
          </p>
          <button class="bg-white border-2 border-black px-6 py-2 font-medium hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
            <a href="/team">
              MEET OUR TEAM
            </a>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-xl mt-8 md:mt-16 mx-auto p-4">
      <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-6">
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
          <Image 
            src={ghanaLogo}
            alt="Amplio Talking Book"
            width={300}
            height={200}
            class="w-[200px] md:w-[300px] object-contain"
          />
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-3 md:mb-4 text-center">Contact Amplio Ghana</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 text-center px-4">Curious about Talking Books? Contact us! We're happy to discuss your project and do a demo. We have offices in Wa and Tamale.</p>
        
        <div class="space-y-2 mb-4 text-center">
          <p>
            <strong>Email:</strong>{' '}
            <a href="mailto:ghana@amplio.org" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline">
              ghana@amplio.org
            </a>
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Phone:</strong>{' '}
            <a href="tel:+233242834803" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline">
              +233 24 283 4803
            </a>
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Phone:</strong>{' '}
            <a href="tel:+233555294412" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-700 hover:underline">
              +233 55 529 4412
            </a>
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-4 text-sm md:text-md text-gray-600 text-center px-4">
          <p>Amplio Ghana is registered with the Registrar General's Department (No: CG059762020) and the Department of Social Welfare (No: 9582) to operate as a non-profit organization in Ghana. TIN: C0049446894</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
</div>